Now...if you are a &quot;dungeon type&quot; it's probably a waste. But if you like hunting in outdoor areas it's just great.<br>
<br>
I never use my horse for travelling (Had Jboots, and now Run3) but I used it during the fights.<br>
There's nothing better than pulling to your Pet, summoning horse and then meditate the whole fight without any disadvantages.<br>
